data.description:
Don't Miss this Opportunity To Own Your Next Home! Prime Southern Location, Approx. 0.25 miles to the Intracoastal Waterway, tucked away in the small Community of Mariners Cove on a low traffic lane. The Home sits on a Large 0.34 acre lot. This Spacious 2,272 sq ft, 1 Story Home, features 3 Bedroom & 2 Bathroom, Office/ Bonus Room, + Multiple Living Spaces, & 2 Car Garage. This home has been recently updated & exudes Charm! From the moment you enter the front door, You will love the open flow of this home, while it uniquely maintains its designated spaces. Shiplap Accent Wall with beautiful wood stained floating shelving flank the fireplace. The formal dining space connects the Office / Bonus Room & the Living Area. The Open Flow of these spaces can easily be made Private (READ MORE)... by the handsome Dual Paneled Wood Stained Barn Doors. The Kitchen has been updated & features Stainless Steel Appliances, with Gas Range, Microwave, Dishwasher, & Refrigerator. The layout provides ample, stunning Quarts counter surface with space to pull up counter stools for entertaining or an informal meal. White wood painted cabinets, white subway tile walls, & bay window add to the charm of this functional Kitchen. Tucked off of the kitchen is a separate, interior Laundry Room with access to the back yard. Washer & Dryer convey with the sale. The home also offers additional living space in the heated & cooled sunroom. Tucked away in the back corner of the home is a spacious Master Bedroom with beautifully updated en suite Master Bathroom with Dual Vanities & garden Tub / Shower. Bead-board Walls add to the charm of the Master Bathroom, with plenty of room to add a freestanding tub & easily add a Separate Walk-in Shower. Master Bedroom also features a large Walk-in Closet. The home also features two Additional well-sized Guest Bedrooms. Additional Full Bathroom has recently been updated with vertical Shiplap Walls, Floating Shelf, & Updated Fixtures. The massive, fenced backyard is ideal for any outdoor hobbies & offers plenty of room to add a pool. The Exterior Storage Building offers appreciate additional storage space. 

Location, Location, Location....  Approx. 9 miles to Navarre Beach, 4 miles to Hurlburt Field Main Gate, & 15 Miles to Eglin AFB Main Gate. Close location to Shopping, Dining, & All the Fun on the Emerald Coast!

For Added Peace of Mind....
Metal Roof was added in 2014, high-end Trane HVAC Installed in 2014, New Gas Water Heater installed in 2018, Ceiling Scraped & Interior Paint done in 2023, Luxury Vinyl Plank Floors were added in 2020, Master Bathroom Remodeled in 2020, Guest Bathroom Remodeled in 2023, & Dishwasher replaced in 2018.

Don't Miss This Opportunity! Call to set-up An In-person or Virtual Showing Today!
